text: Svyatoslav Igorevich Georgiyevsky (; born 26 August 1995) is a Russian professional football player. ==Club career== He made his professional debut on 24 September 2014 for PFC CSKA Moscow in a Russian Cup game against FC Khimik Dzerzhinsk. He made his debut for the main squad of FC Kuban Krasnodar on 23 September 2015 in a Russian Cup game against FC Shinnik Yaroslavl.
